<h1>Route Optimiser</h1>
<section class="content">
  <p>Welcome to the route optimiser page</p>

  <section class="description">
    <p>The route optimiser solves a simple problem, namely:
    <b>"Given a group of people, with a number of vehicles, what is the most
       efficient route between a single point and a collection of points"</b>
    </p>

    <p>Using the app is simple - simply enter the following information:
    <ul>
      <li>The number of drivers, vehicle passenger counts and the divers unique 
          address,</li>
      <li>The unique address of all passengers, and</li>
      <li>The common address and destination of travel, and route optimiser will
          do the rest!</li>
    </p>
  </section>

  <%= link_to "Start now!", drivers_path, :class => "start_button round" %>
</section>
